<paragraph blockId="238.[151,1437,1466,2031]" pageId="238" pageNumber="239">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,427,1574,1599]" pageId="238" pageNumber="239">Range and habitat.</emphasis>
Confirmed specimens are only from the 
<typeStatus box="[886,934,1575,1598]" pageId="238" pageNumber="239">type</typeStatus>
locality. Rios’ report of 
<taxonomicName authority="Woodring, 1928" authorityName="Woodring" authorityYear="1928" class="Gastropoda" family="Drilliidae" genus="Syntomodrillia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="238" pageNumber="239" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="espyra">
<emphasis box="[1208,1311,1575,1599]" italics="true" pageId="238" pageNumber="239">S. espyra</emphasis>
